07786547}}
{"type":"message","id":"a19769d2","parentId":"d066c364","timestamp":"2026-04-10T07:56:48.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking which skills I have loaded. I can see from the available_skills section in the system prompt that I have the following skills available:\n\n1. clawhub - Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com\n2. coding-agent - Delegate coding tasks to Codex, Claude Code, or Pi agents via background process\n3. gemini - Gemini CLI for one-shot Q&A, summaries, and generation\n4. healthcheck - Host security hardening and risk-tolerance configuration for OpenClaw deployments\n5. himalaya - CLI to manage emails via IMAP/SMTP\n6. mcporter - Use the mcporter CLI to list, configure, auth, and call MCP servers/tools directly\n7. node-connect - Diagnose OpenClaw node connection and pairing failures\n8. skill-creator - Create, edit, improve, or audit AgentSkills\n9. tmux - Remote-control tmux sessions for interactive CLIs\n10. weather - Get current weather and forecasts via wttr.in or Open-Meteo\n\nAnd there's also an imap-smtp-email skill in the workspace.\n\nLet me provide a clean answer about the loaded skills.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据当前配置，**已加载的 skills** 有：\n\n| Skill | 用途 |\n|-------|------|\n| **clawhub** | 搜索、安装、更新和发布 agent skills |\n| **coding-agent** | 将编码任务委托给 Codex、Claude Code 或 Pi agents |\n| **gemini** | Gemini CLI 用于问答、摘要和生成 |\n| **healthcheck** | 主机安全加固和风险容忍度配置 |\n| **himalaya** | 通过 IMAP/SMTP 管理邮件的 CLI |\n| **mcporter** | 用于直接调用 MCP servers/tools 的 CLI |\n| **node-connect** | 诊断 OpenClaw 节点连接和配对失败 |\n| **skill-creator** | 创建、编辑、改进或审核 AgentSkills |\n| **tmux** | 远程控制 tmux 会话 |\n| **weather** | 通过 wttr.in 或 Open-Meteo 获取天气和预报 |\n| **imap-smtp-email** | 通过 IMAP/SMTP 读写邮件 |\n\n这些是 OpenClaw 内置/预装的 skills。需要我详细介绍某个 skill 的使用方法吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-wishub-x6-ctyun-cn","model":"GL